recipesJson.name: 3-2-1 Cheeeeese!...Cake (Strawberry)
recipesJson.author: GoombaVapez
recipesJson.description:
This is a simple yet delectable Strawberry cheesecake!

WF Strawberry Cheesecake- a very very good cheesecake flavor. Complete, with creaminess, graininess and a perfect, realistic “cheesy” note as you would expect from a cheesecake.
 
JF Strawberry Sweet- punches the fruit flavor from the WF Strawberry Cheesecake with a bright, sweet blast of additional strawberry.

FA Graham Crust- enhances the crust note of the cheesecake. I chose FA, because to me it is the lightest of the Graham’s in flavor and I’m using it to enhance a crust and not introduce a new one. It adds a bit of AP that I think the WF is missing in the mix, and understandably so, being a complete cheesecake concentrate. 

Any and all feedback is welcomed! Enjoy!
